author: CBS News
title: Speeding spikes during coronavirus lockdown
description: Government stay-at-home orders have led to a dramatic drop in traffic congestion, but a spike in speeding. California's average speed is up 30% on some roads, while Minnesota has seen traffic deaths double. Kris Van Cleave reports from a state police barracks…
